Russia had plans to have secure comms with a new 'revolutionary' radio setup BUT it relies on 4G cell towers lol So that failed and now all Russian comms on the battlefield are done by either walkie-talkie or by phone. The reason Ukraine can hit Russians so accurately with Artillery is because the Russia cell phones are literally giving off their exact grid coords which makes conducting an indirect fire mission easy as fuck.
Even the USMC still used old ass radios with cryptography tech on it
Like these guys can't even use Frequency Hopping, which that alone would save a lot of Russian lives
Lots are talking about it, and you can find videos of Ukraine just using their own cell phones to find Russians and then call in fires
